# Sprint 6 — /public/ is now a build artifact (Astro output + sync'd docs + zip).
# `scripts/build-site.sh` rebuilds it on every prebuild. Nothing in /public/ is
# source-of-truth any more; source lives in site/ (pages/components) and skills/.
# Anchored to project root so Astro's site/public/ static-asset folder still
# tracks design previews and other source-of-truth files committed there.
/public/
src/generated/

